<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style type="text/css">
      /* General Styles */
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      p {
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      a.button {
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      a.button:hover {
        background-color: #0056b3;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        border-radius: 5px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <p>Dear <%= @user.full_name %>,</p>

      <p>We're reaching out because we need your assistance in gathering some important information.</p>

      <p>To ensure we have everything we need, we've created a simple checklist for you to complete. Your input is crucial and will only take a few minutes of your time.</p>

      <p>
        Please click the link below to view and manage your checklist:
        <br/><br/>
        <a href="<%= documents_request_url(@documents_request) %>" target="_blank" class="button">View Checklist</a>
      </p>

      <p>Your prompt response will help us serve you better and ensure everything is in order. If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out.</p>

      <p>Best Regards,</p>
      <p><%= @documents_request.sender.full_name %></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>